title: SC EP:328 Encounters around the Reservation
itunes:title: SC EP:328 Encounters around the Reservation
description: Tom Sewid will be my guest this evening. Tom is a Native Watchman from coastal British Columbia, and recently visited a tribe in Omaha, Nebraska. I have invited the Webster brothers from the tribe to come on the show and talk about what is going on around the reservation.
